sequenceDiagram
    participant Inspector as MCP Inspector<br/>(Browser)
    participant Auth0 as Auth0<br/>(OAuth Provider)
    participant MCP as Apollo MCP Server
    participant GraphQL as GraphQL API

    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: Pre-Registered Client Configuration
    Note right of Inspector: Client ID: G64sNtsNTCRcNV9feUElpf00mO9bwpkg<br/>Client Secret: a6opiEn...4d9w2w9RkZNClNomXxzHo5ngI06...<br/>Redirect URI: http://localhost:6274/oauth/<br/>Scopes: read:schema execute:queries introspect:schema

    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: 1. Initial Connection
    Inspector->>MCP: Connect to http://127.0.0.1:8000/mcp
    MCP-->>Inspector: 401 Unauthorized<br/>+ OAuth metadata discovery
    Note right of MCP: Returns:<br/>- Authorization server URL<br/>- Required scopes<br/>- Bearer token requirements

    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: 2. OAuth Authorization Flow Begins
    Inspector->>Auth0: GET /authorize<br/>?client_id=G64sNts...<br/>&redirect_uri=http://localhost:6274/oauth/<br/>&response_type=code<br/>&scope=read:schema execute:queries<br/>&audience=http://localhost:8000/mcp-example
    
    Auth0->>Inspector: Opens browser with login page
    Note right of Auth0: User authenticates<br/>(if not already logged in)
    
    Inspector->>Auth0: User grants permission
    Auth0-->>Inspector: 302 Redirect to<br/>http://localhost:6274/oauth/?code=BiPRCK...

    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: 3. Token Exchange
    Inspector->>Auth0: POST /oauth/token<br/>{grant_type: authorization_code<br/>client_id: G64sNts...<br/>client_secret: a6opiEn...<br/>code: BiPRCK...<br/>redirect_uri: http://localhost:6274/oauth/}
    
    Auth0->>Auth0: Validate:<br/>- Client credentials<br/>- Authorization code<br/>- Redirect URI match
    
    Auth0-->>Inspector: {access_token: eyJhbGc...<br/>token_type: Bearer<br/>expires_in: 86400}
    Note right of Auth0: JWT token valid for 24 hours

    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: 4. Authenticated Connection
    Inspector->>MCP: Initialize MCP<br/>Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc...
    MCP->>MCP: Validate JWT:<br/>- Signature verification<br/>- Expiration check<br/>- Scope validation
    MCP-->>Inspector: Server capabilities<br/>{tools: {...}, serverInfo: {...}}
    
    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: 5. Tool Execution
    Inspector->>MCP: tools/list<br/>Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc...
    MCP->>MCP: Check token & scopes
    MCP-->>Inspector: Available tools list
    
    Inspector->>MCP: tools/call (execute GraphQL query)<br/>Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGc...
    MCP->>GraphQL: Execute query
    GraphQL-->>MCP: Query results
    MCP-->>Inspector: Tool execution results

    Note over Inspector,GraphQL: 6. Token Refresh (after expiry)
    Inspector->>Auth0: POST /oauth/token<br/>{grant_type: refresh_token<br/>refresh_token: ...}<br/>OR repeat authorization flow
    Auth0-->>Inspector: New access_token
    Inspector->>MCP: Continue with new token